Preconditions:
- The input array `cards` is not null.
- The length of the input array `cards` is greater than or equal to 2.

Postconditions:
- The returned value is an integer.
- If it is possible to have matching cards among the picked cards, the returned value is the minimum number of consecutive cards needed to have a pair of matching cards.
- If it is impossible to have matching cards among the picked cards, the returned value is -1.